sellerAgent.name: Jim Frings Proud Owner of Max

data.description: This stunning, custom-built home sits on just under 1 acre w/in the tranquil Coachman Hills neighborhood. Surrounded by trees & views of both Mt McLaughlin & Roxy Ann, you are located just minutes from historic Jacksonville.  As you enter, the high ceilings & open floorplan welcome you inside. Next, you'll find the living room, w/ oversized windows that let in plenty of light & breathtaking views. The kitchen features granite counters w/ a butcherblock island, walk-in pantry, & newer appliances including a gas cooktop. The primary suite is its own private oasis, w/ a gas fireplace, double walk-in closets, & soaking tub. Downstairs, you will find a family room w/ a wet bar, additional bedroom, bath, & a fully equipped, 354 sq ft gym w/ heat & a/c! With the 3-car garage upstairs & MASSIVE 1,716 Sq ft add'l garage, you'll have enough room to fit all your vehicles, hobbies & even a 40' RV! Enjoy picturesque sunrises while you relax on either of the 2 large decks that overlook the valley!
